+ * ---------------------           |     countsArray   |                 |
+ *          |                      |     mult          |                 |
+ *          |                      |       load temp 3 |                 |
+ *          |                      |       countWidth  |                 |
+ *          |                      ---------------------                 |
+ *          |                                |                           |
+ *          |-------------------------------------------------------------
+ *          v
